description: Returns a list of Synthetics canary runtime versions. For more information, see Canary Runtime Versions.

nested_items.name: RuntimeVersions
nested_items.description: An array of objects that display the details about each Synthetics canary runtime version.

nested_items.name: VersionName
nested_items.description: The name of the runtime version. For a list of valid runtime versions, see Canary Runtime Versions.

nested_items.name: Description
nested_items.description: A description of the runtime version, created by Amazon.

nested_items.name: ReleaseDate
nested_items.description: The date that the runtime version was released.

nested_items.name: DeprecationDate
nested_items.description: If this runtime version is deprecated, this value is the date of deprecation.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: A token that indicates that there is more data available. You can use this token in a subsequent DescribeRuntimeVersions operation to retrieve the next set of results.
